title: Kasey Kahne shares first picture of newborn son Tanner
text:
Kasey Kahne shares first picture of newborn son Tanner 
10:52a ET Posted by Josh Richter - Shake and Bake Crew + FOX Sports Josh Richter - Shake and Bake Crew Share This Story Updated Oct 16, 2015 at 10:22a ET 
Kasey Kahne became a first-time father this week. 
On Thursday, the Hendrick Motorsports driver used his Instagram account to post a picture of Tanner Lee Kahne. A photo posted by Kasey Kahne (@kaseykahne) on Oct 15, 2015 at 8:35pm PDT 
Little Tanner is the latest in the NASCAR baby boom of 2015, joining Brexton Busch and Scarlett Keselowski as potential members of the "NASCAR Next" class of 2033.
